title: Tree Pack 11 (Mobile/PC)
description: A set of 10 optimized tree models for mobile and other platforms
longDescription:
This pack contains a number of trees optimized in an advanced way for your projects. The texture of the leaves of the trees has been professionally atlased with high resolution.


The models are ready to be used in your games and projects by drag and drop.


Each model has the correct UV lightmap for use with Lightmass without overlapping UV's

The leaves are 3d double sided to have proper normal in rendering


=> The mobile version has about 1500~3000 triangles

=> The PC and console version has about 7000 triangles


Also, you can optimize each mobile tree down to about 600 triangles (40% reduction ratio) by using the unreal engine's LOD maker


Update 1 : The mobile version has been released (about 2000 triangles)

Update 2 : Added high Poly version for PC and console (about 7000 triangles)

Update 3 : Updated LOD Settings (4 LODs)


Download Windows Demo


Also is available in the Tree Bundle
